data.title: The Cambridge History of Science Fiction Compress
data.meta_description: The Cambridge History of Science Fiction Compress - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a chronology of science fiction works from 1516 to 1942. It lists the year, author, and title of over 150 science fiction novels, short stories, films, and other works in chronological order. The chronology spans works from Thomas More's Utopia in 1516 to Isaac Asimov's "Foundation" short story in 1942 and covers major science fiction authors and works from that time period.
